@NODE history "TV-Logo Documentation - History"


@{b}6. History@{ub}


@{b}release 1.4@{ub} @{i}(30.09.2000)@{ui}:
  - completely rewritten the scaling routines which should now work better and
    faster
  - fixed a longstanding bug which could cause erratic program behavior after
    canceling the options window
  - fixed a bug which caused unsaved settings to get lost after changing the
    options
  - fixed a bug which caused string gadgets to get emptied after canceling a
    file requester
  - changed the display of demo text to make it more annoying

@{b}release 1.3@{ub} @{i}(23.08.2000)@{ui}:
  - fixed a bug which caused some keyfiles not to be recognised

@{b}release 1.2@{ub} @{i}(18.08.2000)@{ui}:
  - fixed logo display window height issue with NTSC screenmodes
  - implemented keyfile support
  - fixed a bug which caused a crash when the selected font was too big
  - implemented shadow and outline text effects
  - implemented support for multiline text
  - speeded up the program a bit by removing some unnecessary calculations
  - existing user settings don't get overwritten during update any more
  - updated the documentation with new features

@{b}release 1.1@{ub} @{i}(04.08.2000)@{ui}:
  - no more crashes when run from Workbench
  - this guide is now also installed
  - fixed the settings, options and about windows for NTSC screen sizes
  - the keyboard control in the logo display is now performed using the
    intuition messages instead of the raw keyboard reading
  - implemented an option for keyboard layout selection
  - implemented a feature to blank the logo display with a keypress
  - the logo display window now automaticaly gets focus when it is in front

@{b}release 1.0@{ub} @{i}(12.07.2000)@{ui}:
  Initial release


@ENDNODE
